GROUP 15 – WORKSHOP 2  
Project Title: Intelligent Crop Disease Detection System Using Deep Learning  
Supervisor: Ts. Dr. Mazlan Mohamed  
University: Universiti Teknikal Malaysia Melaka (UTeM)  
Course: Bachelor of Computer Science (Artificial Intelligence)

───────────────────────────────────────────────
TEAM ROLES & RESPONSIBILITIES (FINAL VERSION)
───────────────────────────────────────────────

1. ELANGO A/L VELLASAMY (B032310233)
   Role: Team Leader & Mobile App Developer (Module 3 – Results & Recommendations)
   Responsibilities:
   • Lead and coordinate the project workflow, team communication, and weekly progress.
   • Develop the Flutter mobile interface (Home, Upload, Result, About).
   • Integrate the trained TensorFlow Lite model with the Flutter app.
   • Manage GitHub repository, commits, and version control.
   • Conduct integration testing for real-time disease detection.
   • Present the final demo and documentation to the supervisor.

2. YEW ZHI YU (B032310595)
   Role: Model & Dataset Developer (Module 1 & 2 – Image Capture, Preprocessing & CNN Model)
   Responsibilities:
   • Handle dataset collection, cleaning, and preprocessing.
   • Perform image enhancement, noise removal, segmentation, and normalization.
   • Train CNN model using TensorFlow/Keras (MobileNetV2 transfer learning).
   • Convert trained .h5 model to TensorFlow Lite (.tflite) for mobile deployment.
   • Upload model training notebook to GitHub under /notebooks/.
   • Document preprocessing pipeline and model performance results.

3. MUHAMMAD FAIZ BIN MOHD SALLEH (B032420081)
   Role: Model Testing & Evaluation Analyst (Module 3 Support)
   Responsibilities:
   • Validate CNN predictions on test images.
   • Generate confusion matrix, precision, recall, and accuracy reports.
   • Support model performance tuning and dataset analysis.
   • Assist Elango and Yew in integration testing with Flutter + TFLite.
   • Contribute to final project report and result documentation.

4. ABDULAZIZ ALI SALEM AWADH (B032310888)
   Role: Documentation & Integration Support
   Responsibilities:
   • Prepare and compile proposal, report, and presentation slides.
   • Document technical and non-technical project modules.
   • Support integration testing between UI and CNN model.
   • Maintain organized folder structure in GitHub (/docs/).
   • Handle formatting and final submission preparation.

